text: Chionodes permacta is a moth in the family Gelechiidae. It is found in North America, where it has been recorded from western Alaska, southern Yukon and Alberta to Idaho, Wyoming, Montana, Washington, Colorado and southern Oregon.Chionodes at funetmothphotographersgroup ==References== Category:Chionodes Category:Moths described in 1925 Category:Moths of North America
